General.Name: Real Heart
General.Description: Scandinavian Real Heart AB (Publ) designs and develops an artificial heart. It engages in developing Realheart TAH to treat advanced stage heart failure. The company also develops RealVAD, PulsePump, and Sternal Prosthesis products. Scandinavian Real Heart AB (Publ) was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Västerås, Sweden.
